short_description: Design your own perky queen-dom in bedrooms, playrooms, and nurseries with princess wall decals that add a pinch of magic to any space. To apply each majestic maven and her pastoral empire,  simply peel and stick. Arrange and rearrange each repositionable wall sticker to create a uniquely splendid scene with starry skies and lush flower fields. Need to relocate your royal realm? This wall decals kit is removable, reusable, and safe for walls.
faq:
• Q: HOW DO I APPLY WALLCANDY_?
  • A: Application is a simple three-step process of peel, place then smooth with your hand. Your WallCandy can be rearranged and easily removed numerous times. Freshly painted or cleaned walls should be completely dry before applying the product. Completely dry may be longer than you think. In some room environments that could mean a few weeks for every layer to be cured.

  • Q: HOW LONG WILL MY WALLCANDY_ STAY UP ON MY WALL?
  • A: WallCandy is as easy to remove as it is to install but left alone it will stay on your wall for 3-5 glorious, artful years or more.

  • Q: WILL WALLCANDY_ STICK TO ANY WALL IN MY HOUSE?
  • A: WallCandy adheres to most clean and smooth surface.
material: Non-toxic PVC Vinyl with a low tack adhesive. It is non-phthalate, contains no VOC's or lead.

short_description: This is the perfect night-time companion to help soothe your child to sleep in a safe, calming and effortless way. name: Full Size Puzzle Stacker
description:
• Developmental benefits
  • Multi-use (puzzle and stacker)
  • High quality construction
  • Easy to hold rings on extra thick stacking pole
  • Best Toy of the Year - Creative Child - Safe non-toxic paint
short_description:
A Stacker for the Stages - with more developmental benefits.

Children are initially challenged to fine-tune motor skills by placing the easy to hold rings on extra thick stacking pole. With that mastered the child begins to enhance spatial logic by interlocking anyone puzzle piece to any other; in any order. At this point, there is no wrong answer! Finally, through "solving" the puzzle sequence the child learns color and size recognition.

Premium Quality Construction! The stacker pole is thicker than average stackers making the stacker more durable while reducing poking hazards. Each puzzle pieces is cut from a single piece of wood, reducing the possibility of breakage.

With its playful challenges through multiple stages of development and its premium quality wood constructions the P'kolino Puzzle Stacker is likely to be a classic for the ages.

  • P'kolino products meet or exceed US, EU, and Canadian safety standards. For children ages 12 months and up.

short_description: This brand new P'kolino Geared Shape Sorter keeps tiny tots entertained and engaged as they turn the gears and slide chunky, color-coded shapes into this smiling shape sorter character. Infants will enhance their motor skills and learn color and shape recognition as they interact with this fun developmental toy. Made from sturdy plywood with non-toxic, waterbased finishes, the P'kolino Geared Shape Sorter measures 7 x 3.5 x 11 inches. Ages 12 months & up.

name: My Little Seat - Pocket Full of Posies
description:
• Ultra portable and machine washable travel high chair
  • For babies who can sit unassited approximately 6 months up to 35 pounds
  • 5 point harness including extra reinforced fabric and seams
  • Is focused on contemporary, modern and fashionable design
  • Everyone gets a seat at the table with My Little Seat

short_description: My Little Seat is the ultimate infant high chair for traveling with baby in tow. Whether you are using it every day at home, out for lunch with friends or jet setting around the world this super cute and always trendy seat will make your life so much easier and always get you noticed. It is suitable from 6 months and above or when your baby can sit unassisted. Everyone gets a seat at the table with My Little Seat.

name: Puppy Necksaver
description:
• Winner of 3 major awards iParenting Media Outstanding Award, JPMA Innovation Award, CreativeChild Top Choice Award.
  • Made of soft, hypoallergenic material designed to absorb moisture and pamper the baby.
  • Perfect for both the cold as well as the warm months of the year.
  • Ergonomically designed to cradle the baby's head, thereby reducing strain on the neck.
  • Its shape is designed to fit the unique size and shape of an infantﾒs neck.
  • Can be easily used across all platforms; in the car seat, stroller, high chair, swing, or any place where the baby sits.
short_description:
Baberoo NeckSavers -- the most versatile head and neck support for babies. Ergonomically designed to cradle your baby's head and reduce strain in the neck, the NeckSaver enables your baby to rest more comfortably no matter where he is. It can be used in the cars, strollers, swings, bouncers, and high chairs! Winner of 3 major awards iParenting Media Outstanding Award, JPMA Innovation Award, CreativeChild Top Choice Award.

Proper neck support is crucial to young babies as their skeletal structures undergo the greatest development in the early months. With good neck support, babies can develop better postures, are more comfortable, rest better, and wakeup happier.

name: My Little Seat - Coco Snow
description:
• Ultra portable and machine washable travel high chair
  • For babies who can sit unassited approximately 6 months up to 35 pounds
  • 5 point harness including extra reinforced fabric and seams
  • Is focused on contemporary, modern and fashionable design
  • Everyone gets a seat at the table with My Little Seat
short_description: My Little Seat is the ultimate infant high chair for traveling with baby in tow. Whether you are using it every day at home, out for lunch with friends or jet setting around the world this super cute and always trendy seat will make your life so much easier and always get you noticed. It folds down to the size of a diaper and comes with its very own matching bag. My Little Seat is designed with safety in mind and incorporates a 5 point harness along with its extra reinforced seaming and is safety tested for strength and durability. Your baby will love sitting along with you at the table like everyone else. Sling it over a chair and it sets up in seconds and of course is machine washable. It is suitable from 6 months and above or when your baby can sit unassisted. Everyone gets a seat at the table with My Little Seat.
material: 100% cotton canvas, 100% polyester felt applique, 100% polyethylene coating (on inside). Machine Washable

name: Plush Hooded Towel - Bubble Blue Minky
description:
• Top quality materials used in construction. We use the softest and thickest double sided terry cloth, for ultimate comfort and warmth.
  • Terry cloth lines inside of hood to dry head and hair.
  • High quality trim used in construction.
  • Wash and dry with like colors.
  • 110% Mamaky approved! We have one and absolutely love it. One year later, and many, many washes later, it is still thick and soft.
  • Made in the USA.
short_description: Infantissima Hooded bath towels give your young one a sense of comfort because all of our fabrics are gentle, toddler friendly, and are capable of lasting throughout many years of use. The hooded towel was specially created to take care of babies. They use only luxurious high quality terry cloth to quickly remove water from your infant's body. This reduces the chance that your baby will feel cold from the left over moister on his skin.

name: Kaboost Portable Chair - Chocolate
description:
• Winner of multiple awards. An absolute industry darling for design and innovation.
  • Holds up to 136kg or 300lbs
  • Raises the height of 4-legged chairs, allowing child to sit at the table w/ family
  • KABOOST is the seat solution for parents fed up with grubby restaurant booster seats and bulky highchairs
  • Has four spring-loaded arms that fit snugly under the legs of kitchen and dining chairs
  • Two height settings - lifts entire chair either 4.5" or 3.75"
  • Snaps on in seconds. Stays attached even when chair is moved
  • Non-slip, rubberized feet will not scratch floors
  • Weighs just 3.5lbs
    • ?????? ??????
short_description: High chairs and big, bulky booster seats are officially obsolete, thanks to the KABOOST portable chair booster. KABOOST is a one-of-a-kind portable chair booster that raises the height of 4-legged chairs, allowing your 2 to 6 year-old child to sit at the table with the family. KABOOST is the seat solution for parents fed up with grubby restaurant booster seats and bulky highchairs. Instead of raising your child, KABOOST raises the chair itself. This portable, adjustable chair booster has four spring-loaded arms that fit snugly under the legs of kitchen and dining chairs, lifting the entire chair 4.5" or 3.75". KABOOST snaps onto the chair in just seconds, as its spring-loaded arms firmly grip chair legs into place, staying attached even when the chair is moved or repositioned. KABOOST's nonslip, rubberized feet will not scratch floors. Weighing just 3.5 lbs, as lightweight and compact as it is, KABOOST is extremely sturdy, holding up to 300 lbs. and is engineered to improve chair stability.

name: Sleep Sheep with Smart Sensor
description:
• 4 Soothing Sounds: Mother's Heartbeat, Spring Showers, Ocean Waves and Whale Songs
  • Automatically plays sound when sensor detects baby cry
  • Velcro tab to secure Sleep Sheep to the outside of a crib
  • The Sleep Sheep story & numbered adoption certificate
  • Two AA batteries included
  • Ideal for newborns and up
    • Brand VIDEO
short_description: This version of the popular Sleep Sheep series automatically plays sound of choice when the sensor detects the baby cry. It's the perfect night-time companion to help soothe your child to sleep in a safe, calming and effortless way. A sound box is tucked safely inside the plush sheep. The sheep plays four peaceful sounds, including Mother's Heartbeat, Spring Showers, Ocean Waves and Whale Songs. A Velcro tab secures the Sleep Sheep to the outside of your babyﾒs crib for a calming, constant buffer that blocks out exterior or unwanted sound.

name: Blue Twilight Turtle
description:
• Newly released blue color plush and shell
  • Transforms your room into a starry night
  • Projects 8 different constellations on ceiling and walls
  • 3 Color options: amber, blue, and green
  • Nightlight helps ease fear of the dark
  • 45-Minute sleep timer
  • Illustrated star constellation guide
  • Uses 3 AAA batteries (included).
    • Brand VIDEO
short_description:
Twilight Turtle is a plush toy that transforms any room into a starry night sky to help comfort children to sleep. From within his plastic shell, Twilight Turtle projects a magical constellation of stars onto bedroom ceiling and walls in three soothing color options. Twilight Turtle's shell illuminates to help ease children's fear of the dark. 

This interactive and educational toy includes eight actual constellations (such as The Big Dipper) embedded in the star pattern. Parents can sit with their children and identify these major constellations using the wonderfully illustrated Twilight Turtle Star Guide. Twilight Turtle helps make bedtime fun for children 3 and up.

  • Batteries included (three AAA batteries)

short_description: Tranquil Turtle helps kids fall asleep, by recreating the soothing sights and sounds of the ocean at calm. The light projector creates a serene underwater effect - complete with softly undulating waves - while the sound machine unit offers two calming choices: a gentle melody or whispering waves. A great solution for kids who are afraid of the dark. With adjustable brightness and auto shut-off. Winner of the National Parenting Center Seal of Approval

name: Boy Footie (Blue/Grey/Lime) Newborn
short_description: Lynne Buchman wanted to be a more attentive auntie to her nephews, so she made them a gift. That's how this adorable brand got started. From one gift, Loralin Design evolved to include a wide range of products and apparel. Since the beginning, people have been drawn to Buchman's simple forms and innovative color combinations and we're sure you will too!

name: 8oz Daisy's 2-in-1 Organic Shampoo/Body Wash
description:
• Made in USA using domestic and foreign ingredients.
  • Great for kids with eczema or sensitive skin.
  • Plant-based, non-irritating cleansers, get your baby squeaky clean without irritating eyes or skin.
  • Fresh light citrus natural scent derived from essential oils.
  • Full of nourishing and calming organic botanicals including olive oil, aloe, and pure essential oils.
  • Not tested on animals.
short_description:
Lather up like Daisy and come out smelling like flowers! A pure and natural formula that combines gentle, organic plant-based cleansers with nourishing, calming, and moisturizing olive oil and aloe to create an all-in-one wash for babies and toddlers. 

This gentle wash is perfect for sensitive skin, cradle cap, or eczema and will leave your little ones soft as silk and smelling clean. Reuse the bottle made of 100% recycled plastic for a truly sustainable bath time experience.

Most of our ingredients are locally sourced from organic farms in California and the Pacific Northwest. Those that are not produced locally come from Germany.
material: Completely free of genetically modified organisms, parabens, petrochemicals, phthalates, sulfates, synthetic dyes, synthetic fragrances, triclosan or preservatives./100% recycled and reusable plastic bottle.

name: 12 oz Dewey's Organic Natural Baby Bubble Bath
description:
• Made in USA using domestic and foreign ingredients.
  • Big, big bubbles that kids love to play with
  • All-natural and extremely mild plant-based cleansers
  • No slippery residue left on skin or tub
  • Rich in organic botanicals including aloe, plantain & white peony tea extracts, & pure essential oils
  • Not tested on animals
short_description:
Deweyﾒs bubbles are the best! This pure, natural formula combines plant-based cleansers and botanicals to create mountains of big bubbles for bath-time fun and relaxation. 

Organic aloe, plantago extract, and white peony tea extract nourish the skin while the cleansers gently remove germs and dirt. Mild, fresh, and clean organic essential oils make the bath smell terrific! Reuse the bottle made of 100% recycled plastic for a truly sustainable bath time experience.

Most of our ingredients are locally sourced from organic farms in California and the Pacific Northwest. Those that are not produced locally come from Germany.
material: Completely free of genetically modified organisms, parabens, petrochemicals, phthalates, sulfates, synthetic dyes or fragrances, triclosan & preservatives/100% recycled and reusable plastic bottle

name: 8 oz Clio's "Beary" Soft Organic Lotion
description:
• Made in USA using domestic and foreign ingredients.
  • Excellent to help heal eczema or damaged skin
  • Great for sunburns and sore bottoms
  • Truly unique formula based on organic sunflower oil infused with a multitude of calming and healing organic herbs
  • Also contains organic shae butter and bees wax
  • Beautiful natural scent from herbal infusion (no added scent)
short_description:
Clio's lotion is a truly unique formula that combines organic sunflower oil infused with a multitude of calming and healing organic herbs with shea butter, aloe and bees wax in a formula that is over 80% organic. 

It calms sunburns, rashes, eczema and other skin irritations the natural and organic way. Moms love it as much as kids do! Reuse the bottles made of 100% recycled plastic for a truly sustainable bath time experience.

Most of our ingredients are locally sourced from organic farms in California and the Pacific Northwest. Those that are not produced locally come from Germany.
material: Completely free of genetically modified organisms, parabens, petrochemicals, phthalates, harmful sulfates, synthetic dyes or fragrances, triclosan & harsh preservaties

name: 8 oz Ollie's Super Sudsy Organic Hand Soap
description:
• Made in USA using domestic and foreign ingredients.
  • Purified water, aloe leaf juice*, decyl glucoside**, sodium coco sulfate**, lauryl lactyl lactate, plantago extract*, white peony tea extract*, natural scent, citric acid, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate *Certified organic ingredient from organic farm in California or the Pacific Northwest or **Ecocert ingredient from Germany.

  • Most of our ingredients are locally sourced from organic farms in California and the Pacific Northwest. Those ingredients that are not produced locally come from Germany. See how short our ingredients list is? That is all you need! No inexpensive fillers - just top quality essentials.

This gentle wash is perfect for dry, sensitive skin, or eczema and will leave your little ones' hands soft as silk and smelling clean.   Most of our ingredients are locally sourced from organic farms in California and the Pacific Northwest. Those that are not produced locally come from Germany.

name: Swiss Dot w/Pink Woven RuffleButt 0-3mo
description:
• Adds a touch of innocence to any outfit.
  • Mix and match with any outfit in her closet. Or put this on over her diaper...and voila, she's dressed and ready to go!
  • Made of 100% cotton and machine washable, this is designed for the stylish, yet busy mom. And really, what mom isn't busy?!
  • The Swiss Dot Embroidery has contrasting pink fabric ruffles and is absolutely precious in person!
short_description: One of our most popular Bloomers, the unique, embroidered detail in this soft, white fabric really sets it apart from the rest! With pink, anti-wrinkle ruffles, this sweet bloomer is perfect for pictures, or just a day at the park.

name: Medium Blue Girls Denim Jacket 18-24mos
short_description: Fully lined and a little frilly, this chilly weather go-to is perfect for your cutie patootie. We took the denim jacket wardrobe staple and added some fun RuffleButts flair! description:
• 8oz baby bottle has a 4 scoop formula capacity

  • Makes bottle feeding easy
  • To use: Place formula in compartment and water in bottle, then push the button and shake well to mix
  • Patented, airtight compartment
  • Compartment lid is free-floating agitator that mixes formula and prevents clumps
  • Vented nipples minimize colic
  • Dishwasher- and microwave-safe
  • BPA-, phthalate- and PVC-free
  • 100% silicone nipple
  • Polypropylene bottle
short_description: A baby bottle that can be prepared now and mixed later? Yes, and Mixie is her name. This smart, formula-mixing baby bottle with its patented, air-tight design will not leak. Put formula in the little compartment, water in the bottle and when the babyﾒs ready, push the button to release powder, shake and blend. Simple.

name: Gears! Gears! Gears!® Beginner's Building Set
description:
• Features 95 sturdy plastic pieces that snap together and are compatible with all other Gears! Gears! Gears!® building sets
  • Encourages creativity while building fine motor skills in hands-on construction play
  • Provides easy-to-follow, color-coded building instructions and also allows kids to improvise—there’s no wrong way to build!
  • Includes spinning gears, pillars, connectors, cranks to set creations in motion and interlocking plates for limitless building
  • Ages 3+
short_description: GEARS! GEARS! GEARS!® is a child's introduction to the world of construction and movement. Bright colors and easy-to-assemble pieces encourage children to create moving masterpieces. There are so many ways to build, children discover something new every time they play!

name: Simple Tape Measure
short_description: Perfectly-sized tape measure for little explorers! Your kids will love working with this perfectly-sized, manual-wind tape measure. Appealing, contemporary design and simplified features (inches and feet on one side of the tape, centimeters and meter on the other). Measures up to 4 feet—perfect for comparing heights!

name: Teaching Cash Register
description:
• Rewards transactions with lights, sounds and voice messages
  • Holds actual-size money and includes play coins and bills, coupon and credit card
  • Features a built-in scanner, scale and coin slot
  • Helps children practice coin recognition, addition, subtraction and place value with 4 engaging games
  • Offers volume control
  • Additional money available (LER 2645)
  • Prolongs battery life with automatic shut-off feature
  • Requires 3 C batteries, not included
short_description: The Teaching Cash Register is a fun and exciting way for children to explore the concept of money while using theirimaginations. This unique educational toy features games and play patterns that familiarize children, from pre-school on up, with the size and value of certain coins. Children will naturally begin learning to add and subtract when they use the Teaching Cash Register for pretend play, as they buy and sell items from their pretend store.

name: Teaching Telephone
description:
• Experts agree that it’s important for kids to learn phone skills early. Make it fun!
  • Encourages children to learn their home phone number and how to dial 911 in case of an emergency through interactive play
  • Allows you to easily program in numbers you want children to learn and record reward messages they’ll hear when they dial correctly
  • Also plays preprogrammed messages children hear when they dial a number correctly
  • Invites imaginative play that also supports oral language development
  • Features realistic ring and design, with big buttons for little hands
  • Boosts children’s confidence in life skills
  • Includes holder for standard 3"L x 2"H notepaper
  • Requires 3 AA batteries, included
short_description: The Pretend & Play® Teaching Telephone™ is great for teaching children important telephone numbers and skills. This unique toy telephone has program and record features to help you teach your child important telephone numbers while he or she is having fun! Use the Teaching Telephone to help your child learn about 911 emergency services, telephone manners (including answering and speaking on the telephone), and even taking messages. The Teaching Telephone is designed so parents can program in telephone numbers and record messages for young children. Older children can program and record messages on their own.

name: Velvet Kilt (Deep Mysterious Purple Creme)
description:
• Non-toxic alternative to solvent-based nail polish
  • Next generation formula with a richer consistency for smoother application and better coverage.
  • Water-based formula is free of the harsh, smelly chemicals and contains none of the chemicals found in typical nail polish
  • We are "3 Free" as well as free of ethyl acetate, butyl acetate, nitrocellulose, acetone, and heavy metals.
short_description:
Scotch Naturals™ polish has a lot in common with the women who wear it. We are smart, fun, and forward thinking. We care about the environment, and we come in a wide variety of colors. When we want to look and feel our best, we choose natural products, knowing it’s not just healthier for us, but for the world around us. 

Making the change to non-toxic nail polish is one you won’t regret. Scotch Naturals is a safe and eco-friendly alternative to conventional polish. Our revolutionary water-based formula delivers long lasting, salon-quality results in a stunning array of sophisticated shades. 

Our polishes contain none of the chemicals found in typical nail polish. We are “3 Free” as well free of ethyl acetate, butyl acetate, nitrocellulose, acetone, and heavy metals. We are truly non-toxic.
material: free of ethyl acetate, butyl acetate, nitrocellulose, acetone, and heavy metals.
warnings:
For the Perfect Finish

In order to achieve beautiful, healthy, salon-quality nails it is essential to prep them properly:
1. Remove any existing nail polish and shape as usual.
2. Add a drop of jojoba oil to each nail and buff gently.
3. Wash hands with soap and water to rinse remover residue and buffing dust.
4. Apply 1 coat of our fortifying base coat.
5. Follow with 2 coats of polish allowing 1-3 minutes in between coats.
6. Finish with our deluxe/top coat for a high gloss shine.

Please remember, this is a water-based nail product. While it dries to the touch in minutes, it needs a few hours to cure fully prior to prolonged exposure to water. We encourage painting tips and toes before bed, allowing polish to dry and adhere overnight.

Making the change to non-toxic nail polish is one you won’t regret. Scotch Naturals is a safe and eco-friendly alternative to conventional polish. Our revolutionary water-based formula delivers long lasting, salon-quality results in a stunning array of sophisticated shades. 

Our polishes contain none of the chemicals found in typical nail polish. We are “3 Free” as well free of ethyl acetate, butyl acetate, nitrocellulose, acetone, and heavy metals. We are truly non-toxic.
material: free of ethyl acetate, butyl acetate, nitrocellulose, acetone, and heavy metals.
warnings:
For the Perfect Finish

In order to achieve beautiful, healthy, salon-quality nails it is essential to prep them properly:
1. Remove any existing nail polish and shape as usual.
2. Add a drop of jojoba oil to each nail and buff gently.
3. Wash hands with soap and water to rinse remover residue and buffing dust.
4. Apply 1 coat of our fortifying base coat.
5. Follow with 2 coats of polish allowing 1-3 minutes in between coats.
6. Finish with our deluxe/top coat for a high gloss shine.

Please remember, this is a water-based nail product. While it dries to the touch in minutes, it needs a few hours to cure fully prior to prolonged exposure to water. We encourage painting tips and toes before bed, allowing polish to dry and adhere overnight.

name: Hot Dots Jr. "Ace" the Talking Teaching Dog Pen
description:
• Engages your youngest learners with easy–to–use technology—simply press the pen down on the cards to answer and receive feedback
  • Allows independent, self–paced reinforcement and review of key early learning topics
  • Provides opportunity for students to prepare for school, or catch up where they need support
  • Activity Card Sets (available separately) include 36 colorfully illustrated double–sided cards providing 72 early learning activities plus an answer key all stored in a handled carrying case
  • Ace unit requires 2 AAA batteries (not included) and measures 6"L
  • Grades PreK+
short_description: Part learning companion, part magic wand, the Hot Dots Jr. Pen talks, laughs, lights up and even buzzes with excitement as children explore. Designed for little hands, this electronic pen cheers for correct answers and gently redirects children when they answer incorrectly, allowing for independent discovery.
